!caution  This is A GAME, DON'T do ANY HACK

simulate iOS-like OS on your hand.

build your own defense system.
Develop new code by hands.

The feature:
  * some tutorial
  * not serious, but serial story mode
  * original language(based on exist language)
    * or, support many language
  * seek mode (collect users who passed by)
  * zero k (real time battle based on GPS)
  * zero day ( new bugs will be added for each update)
  * don't force to update! decide on your way to defend.


* story mode
  the story is simple.( but I don't write any script yet)

* original language
  In the app, user can write code to develop new system.
  As this app has original language, all people shold start from the same line.

  And also, those who don't want to write code, there's another way.
    1. purchase at User's market
  or
    2. Use visualized editor

* User's market
  At the market, you can purchase other's code to build system or in-app app.
  For example, you can make game and sell them, buy new exploit to attack, buy new defense app.
  But be careful, THOSE COULD BE THE VIRUS.
  so you can make new game Including VIRUS, and sell them.


* builtin apps
  builtin applications by default are:
    * Message (only fixed phrases)
    * Picture (Just see?)
    * Camera (can't take any real Picture)
    * setting
    * apps store( not User's market)

  at first, you should find the way to 
    * write your code
    * the User's market
    * get some useful tools
    * jailbreak your simOS
    * hide you from the awfulness network


some day feature:
  * bot policeman
  * hackers who was employed by police or etc.
  * Police side OS(to break in)
  * educational documents(history of computer, etc)
  * fight against the gamemaster
